        "property":         [
            {"proptype":             {
                "@col-index": "1",
                "p": {"$": "Detergents marked as \"organic\" or \"ecological\" (environmentally friendly) generally contain lower levels of active agents or completely dispense with certain substances. The cleaning effect may be restricted here."}
            }},
            {"proptype":             {
                "@col-index": "1",
                "p": {"$": "Set the rinse aid and the water softening system to the separate detergent or combined detergent in use."}
            }},
            {"proptype":             {
                "@col-index": "1",
                "p": {"$":                 [
                    "According to manufacturers, combined detergents with salt replacement substances can only be used up to a certain water hardness, usually",
